      "text": [
        " : \"إِنْ أَرْسَلْتَ بَازاً أَوْ صَقْراً أَوْ عُقَاباً فَقَتَلَ فَلاَ تَأْكُلْ حَتَّى تُذَكِّيَهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4143 - Abu Basir narrated from Abu Abdillah (as) that Imam (as) said:\n\"If you release a hawk, a falcon, or an eagle and it kills, do not eat it until you properly slaughter it.\""
        ]
